title: Mr. Belani receives the President of the European Union Agency for Criminal Justice Cooperation
text: The Secretary General of the Ministry of Foreign Affairs and the National Community abroad, Mr. Amar Belani received Tuesday the President of the European Union Agency for Criminal Justice Cooperation, Ladislav Hamran.

This meeting comes within the framework of the discussions held Monday by the President of the Republic, Mr. Abdelmadjid Tebboune with the High Representative of the European Union (EU) for Foreign Affairs and Security Policy and Vice-President of the European Commission, Mr. Josep Borrell.
